-- WORLD COLOR: tints the map's ambient lighting with the chosen color.
-- Uses a dedicated ColorCorrectionEffect under Lighting so we can restore
-- the map's original look instantly when disabled. A persistence loop
-- reapplies TintColor / Saturation / Enabled every 0.25s so the map's
-- own lighting scripts can't drift or disable our effect.
